testcase.purpose: Test checks that the frame initiator type is represented
Test checks that resources with data: URIs aren't present in the Resource Timing buffer
Test checks that window.performance is defined
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByName is defined
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByType is defined
Test checks that window.performance.getEntries is defined
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByName('http://.../resource_timing_test0.xml') returns a PerformanceEntry object
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByName('resource_timing_test0.png') returns a PerformanceEntry object
Test checks that PerformanceEntry has correct name, initiatorType, startTime, and duration
Test checks that PerformanceEntry('/resource_timing_test0.png') has correct order of timing attributes
Test checks that PerformanceEntry object is the same when calling via getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.png')
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByName('resource_timing_test0.css') returns a PerformanceEntry object
Test checks that PerformanceEntry returned by window.performance.getEntriesByName('resource_timing_test0.css') has correct name, initiatorType, startTime, and duration.
Test checks that PerformanceEntry(resource_timing_test0.css) has correct order of timing attributes.
Test checks that PerformanceEntry object is the same when calling via getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.css') and getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.css', 'resource')
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.html') returns a PerformanceEntry object
Test checks that PerformanceEntry returned by window.performance.getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.html') has correct name, initiatorType, startTime, and duration
Test checks that PerformanceEntry('http://127.0.0.1http://.../resource_timing_test0.html') has correct order of timing attributes.
Test checks that PerformanceEntry object is the same when calling via getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.html')
Test checks that window.performance.getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.js') returns a PerformanceEntry object
Test checks that PerformanceEntry returned by window.performance.getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.js') has correct name, initiatorType, startTime, and duration
Test checks that PerformanceEntry('/resource_timing_test0.js') has correct order of timing attributes.
Test checks that PerformanceEntry object is the same when calling via getEntriesByName('/resource_timing_test0.js')
Test checks that Only 1 PerformanceEntry should match
Test checks that redirectStart should be 0
Test checks that redirectEnd should be 0
Test checks that fetchStart should be non-zero
Test checks that domainLookupStart should be greater than or equal to fetchStart
Test checks that domainLookupEnd should be greater than or equal to domainLookupStart
Test checks that connectStart should be greater than or equal to domainLookupEnd
Test checks that connectEnd should be greater than or equal to connectStart
Test checks that requestStart should be greater than or equal to connectEnd
Test checks that responseStart should be greater than or equal to requestStart
Test checks that responseEnd should be greater than or equal to responseStart
Test checks that a 304 Not Modified resource appears in the buffer
Test checks that connectStart and connectEnd are the same when a connection is reused
Test checks that the link initiator type is represented even when dynamically inserted
Test checks that the img initiator type is represented even when dynamically inserted
Test checks that the iframe initiator type is represented even when dynamically inserted
Test checks that iframes that navigate themselves don't appear in the buffer
Test checks that failed resources aren't present in the Resource Timing buffer
